ssage\", \"from\": 3209, \"to\": 3218}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Naturally, we had to take into account the international community.\", \"from\": 3243, \"to\": 3311, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"account\", \"from\": 3275, \"to\": 3282}, {\"ngram\": \"the international community\", \"from\": 3283, \"to\": 3310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having said that - it is a French ceremony for the French Games - so we trusted our artistic director.\", \"from\": 3312, \"to\": 3414, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3339, \"end\": 3345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.986270120799058, \"rank\": 0.007823375404590124, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the French Games\", \"from\": 3359, \"to\": 3375}, {\"ngram\": \"our artistic director\", \"from\": 3392, \"to\": 3413}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have freedom of expression in France and we wanted to protect it.\\\"\", \"from\": 3415, \"to\": 3484, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3448, \"end\": 3454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9970901524296049, \"rank\": 0.0027911518242900884, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"freedom\", \"from\": 3423, \"to\": 3430}, {\"ngram\": \"expression\", \"from\": 3434, \"to\": 3444}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 spokesperson Anne Descamps told a press conference: \\\"Clearly there was never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group.\", \"from\": 3486, \"to\": 3629, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3486, \"end\": 3496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7816382489663845e-21, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.or